<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT12">
<l>neñcurukik kaṇpaṉippa niṟkuñ cōrum</l>
<l>neṭituyirkku muṇṭaṟiyā ḷuṟakkam pēṇāḷ</l>
<l>nañcaravil tuyilamarnta nampī yeṉṉum</l>
<l>vampārpūm vayalāli maintā yeṉṉum</l>
<l>añciṟaiya puṭkoṭiyē yāṭum pāṭu</l>
<l>maṇiyaraṅka māṭutumō tōḻī yeṉṉum</l>
<l>eñciṟakiṉ kīḻaṭaṅkāp peṇṇaip peṟṟē</l>
<l>ṉirunilattōr paḻipaṭaittē ṉēpā vammē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She stands [stricken] as her eyes stream, her heart melting; she languishes;</l>
<l rend="indent">she sighs at length; she ignores food [and] cares not [for] sleep.</l>
<l>I begot this girl who says, “Noble who rests [in yogic] sleep on the poisonous snake,”</l>
<l rend="indent">who says, “Young man of Āli with fields of flowers full of fragrance,”</l>
<l>Who says, “Friend, shall we dance in ornate Araṅkam</l>
<l rend="indent">where they dance [and] sing of the banner with a fine winged  bird,”</l>
<l>And who is not restrained under my wing.</l>
<l rend="indent">I gained the blame of [all of] those in the vast world. Alas!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
